    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/8f6d4fb3b594945457c2938c65be4d01.poster.avif?t=1769966619\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/8f6d4fb3b594945457c2938c65be4d01.webm?t=1769966619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/8f6d4fb3b594945457c2938c65be4d01.mp4?t=1769966619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shadow Eclipse</strong> is an action roguelite dungeon crawler built around magic, mastery, and replayability. Wield powerful spells, experiment with unique build combinations, and fight through a world consumed by shadow. Each run challenges you to adapt and push deeper into increasingly dangerous depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/2fb194583579ee7fa6bdeb1624e8a35a.poster.avif?t=1769966619\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/2fb194583579ee7fa6bdeb1624e8a35a.webm?t=1769966619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425670/extras/2fb194583579ee7fa6bdeb1624e8a35a.mp4?t=1769966619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Combat:</strong> Battle through escalating enemy encounters and hostile environments as difficulty increases with each level. Powerful bosses guard the path forward and test your build, timing, and control of magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Diversity:</strong> Each room cleared rewards randomized spell upgrades, ensuring no two runs play the same. Your mage can only wield three spells at a time, forcing you to choose which abilities to keep as your build evolves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Astral Lens:</strong> A mysterious device lets you influence the balance of light and darkness before each run. Shifting the world toward one side increases danger — enemies grow stronger, encounters become more volatile, and survival demands greater mastery. The further you tilt the balance, the harsher the eclipse becomes.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 unique spells</strong>, each with distinct mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+ upgrades</strong> that modify and enhance spells</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10+ enemy types</strong> with varied behaviors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 boss fights</strong> that block progression into deeper areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Astral Lens Runs:</strong> Only Light Run I is dev complete - 5 more runs are in development.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
